{"id": 1858, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你觉得人们对“有个性”有哪些误解？", "description": "还有哪些跑偏了的“放飞自我”型不自知，请在留言区一并揭发。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 22193, "comment_count": 57, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201708171212118yJwov9XWfTUCA4p.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-17T17:00:35Z", "questions": [{"id": 2821, "title": "现如今，你觉得人们对“有个性”有哪些误解？", "content": "现如今，你觉得人们对“有个性”有哪些误解？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 229918, "content": "把小众等同于个性：不看大众电影，不听流行音乐，不看畅销小说", "image": "img/option/option/20170817122143VvF6TroIjuGZBDpw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229920, "content": "用段子粉饰懒、丑、胖、没毅力，并乐于标榜，超出自嘲范畴", "image": "img/option/option/20170817122207KPQpux7bMy2Sr4Lm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229928, "content": "把直率和有个性等同，好恶由心，心直口快", "image": "img/option/option/20170817122507sv1BoYTcdaz3thlG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229929, "content": "为了追求刻意的个性，而掩饰与他人的共性", "image": "img/option/option/20170817122538dokHgNlG483eDrs7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229930, "content": "做无意义的猎奇/危险的事来标新，“就要做别人没做过的”", "image": "img/option/option/20170817122920cPEqk6HhrlLRYeIC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229932, "content": "漠视一切规则：把无礼当自由、把傲慢当自信", "image": "img/option/option/20170817122717jK27bOEViGoMkU4t.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229934, "content": "过度抖机灵，哪儿都想显幽默，不解决真正的问题", "image": "img/option/option/20170817122836qVBcpTbJ3mt0KFuy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 229925, "content": "“我就是我”：我固执己见，我做自己，我没什么要改的", "image": "img/option/option/201708171224243lJLvgUtmVzpORQS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}